==English==
===Etymology===
(Mid 19th or 20th century) American Spanish ''[[cafetería]]'', [[coffeehouse]], from ''[[cafetera]]'', coffee maker, from French ''[[cafetière]]'', from ''[[café]]'', from Ottoman Turkish ''qahveh''

===Noun===
'''cafeteria'''

#A place where they have food or lunch in schools.

====Related terms====
